profile.bio:
Joep is a VCDX-certified (#101), vExpert, EMC Elect, Nutanix Technology Champion and Veeam Vanguard-awarded CTO at OGD ict-diensten. 
Joep is very active in the virtualization and storage community, NLVMUG Leader and writes on his blog, VirtualLifestyle.
